        <mxCell id="ZR-NAflUI1GGsINpZlQH-21" parent="1" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=light-dark(#A20025,#FFFFFF);strokeColor=light-dark(#000000,#000000);strokeWidth=3;fontColor=light-dark(#000000,#000000);align=left;verticalAlign=middle;fontSize=25;" value="&lt;span data-path-to-node=&quot;2,2,1,0&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-path-to-node=&quot;1,2,0,0&quot;&gt;&lt;b data-path-to-node=&quot;1,2,0,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot;&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-path-to-node=&quot;1,2,1,0&quot;&gt;Gestão Desportiva e Operacional&lt;/span&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="60" width="1260" x="491" y="-460" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="ZR-NAflUI1GGsINpZlQH-23" parent="1" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=light-dark(#A20025,#FFFFFF);strokeColor=light-dark(#000000,#000000);strokeWidth=3;fontColor=light-dark(#000000,#000000);align=left;verticalAlign=middle;fontSize=25;" value="&lt;span data-path-to-node=&quot;2,2,1,0&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-path-to-node=&quot;1,4,0,0&quot;&gt;&lt;b data-path-to-node=&quot;1,4,0,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot;&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-path-to-node=&quot;1,4,1,0&quot;&gt;Treinadores (Registo) e Atletas / Encarregados de Educação (Consulta)&lt;/span&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="60" width="1260" x="491" y="-400" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="ZR-NAflUI1GGsINpZlQH-24" parent="1" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=light-dark(#A20025,#FFFFFF);strokeColor=light-dark(#000000,#000000);strokeWidth=3;fontColor=light-dark(#000000,#000000);align=left;verticalAlign=middle;fontSize=25;" value="&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;O sistema deve permitir aos treinadores o registo rápido e intuitivo da assiduidade (presenças, faltas&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;justificadas e faltas injustificadas) dos atletas em cada sessão de treino. Simultaneamente, deve disponibilizar&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;aos atletas e encarregados de educação a consulta do seu próprio histórico de presenças." vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="160" width="1260" x="491" y="-340" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="ZR-NAflUI1GGsINpZlQH-25" parent="1" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=light-dark(#A20025,#601414);strokeColor=light-dark(#000000,#000000);movable=1;resizable=1;rotatable=1;deletable=1;editable=1;locked=0;connectable=1;strokeWidth=3;align=center;fontColor=default;fontSize=30;" value="Nome do Requisito" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="60" width="280" x="210" y="-520" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="ZR-NAflUI1GGsINpZlQH-26" parent="1" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=light-dark(#A20025,#601414);strokeColor=light-dark(#000000,#000000);movable=1;resizable=1;rotatable=1;deletable=1;editable=1;locked=0;connectable=1;strokeWidth=3;align=center;fontColor=default;fontSize=30;" value="Ator Principal" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="60" width="280" x="210" y="-399" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="ZR-NAflUI1GGsINpZlQH-27" parent="1" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=light-dark(#A20025,#601414);strokeColor=light-dark(#000000,#000000);movable=1;resizable=1;rotatable=1;deletable=1;editable=1;locked=0;connectable=1;strokeWidth=3;align=center;fontColor=default;fontSize=30;" value="Descrição" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="160" width="280" x="210" y="-340" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="ZR-NAflUI1GGsINpZlQH-28" parent="1" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=light-dark(#A20025,#601414);strokeColor=light-dark(#000000,#000000);movable=1;resizable=1;rotatable=1;deletable=1;editable=1;locked=0;connectable=1;strokeWidth=3;align=center;fontColor=default;fontSize=30;" value="Prioridade" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="60" width="280" x="210" y="-180" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="ZR-NAflUI1GGsINpZlQH-29" parent="1" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=light-dark(#A20025,#601414);strokeColor=light-dark(#000000,#000000);movable=1;resizable=1;rotatable=1;deletable=1;editable=1;locked=0;connectable=1;strokeWidth=3;align=center;fontColor=default;fontSize=30;" value="Pré-condições" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="240" width="280" x="210" y="-120" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="ZR-NAflUI1GGsINpZlQH-30" parent="1" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=light-dark(#A20025,#601414);strokeColor=light-dark(#000000,#000000);movable=1;resizable=1;rotatable=1;deletable=1;editable=1;locked=0;connectable=1;strokeWidth=3;align=center;fontColor=default;fontSize=30;" value="Pós-condições" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="270" width="280" x="210" y="120" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="ZR-NAflUI1GGsINpZlQH-31" parent="1" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=light-dark(#A20025,#601414);strokeColor=light-dark(#000000,#000000);movable=1;resizable=1;rotatable=1;deletable=1;editable=1;locked=0;connectable=1;strokeWidth=3;align=center;fontColor=default;fontSize=30;" value="Critérios de Aceitação" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="290" width="280" x="210" y="390" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="ZR-NAflUI1GGsINpZlQH-32" parent="1" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=light-dark(#A20025,#FFFFFF);strokeColor=light-dark(#000000,#000000);strokeWidth=3;fontColor=light-dark(#000000,#000000);align=left;verticalAlign=middle;fontSize=25;" value="&lt;blockquote style=&quot;margin: 0 0 0 40px; border: none; padding: 0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span data-path-to-node=&quot;1,6,0,0&quot;&gt;&lt;b data-path-to-node=&quot;1,6,0,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot;&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-path-to-node=&quot;1,6,1,0&quot;&gt;Alta&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="60" width="1260" x="491" y="-180" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="ZR-NAflUI1GGsINpZlQH-33" parent="1" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=light-dark(#A20025,#FFFFFF);strokeColor=light-dark(#000000,#000000);strokeWidth=3;fontColor=light-dark(#000000,#000000);align=left;verticalAlign=middle;fontSize=25;" value="&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;1,7,1,0&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;1. O utilizador que faz o registo tem de estar autenticado com perfil de Treinador e associado à respetiva&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;equipa/turma.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;1,7,1,2&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;2. A sessão de treino já se encontra previamente criada e agendada no calendário do sistema.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;1,7,1,4&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;3. Os atletas a avaliar têm de estar formalmente inscritos na modalidade e escalão corretos.&lt;/p&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="240" width="1260" x="491" y="-120" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="ZR-NAflUI1GGsINpZlQH-34" parent="1" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=light-dark(#A20025,#FFFFFF);strokeColor=light-dark(#000000,#000000);strokeWidth=3;fontColor=light-dark(#000000,#000000);align=left;verticalAlign=middle;fontSize=25;" value="&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;1,8,1,0&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;1. O registo de assiduidade é persistido na base de dados e o estado da sessão de treino passa a&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&quot;Realizada/Concluída&quot;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;1,8,1,2&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;2. As estatísticas individuais de assiduidade do atleta (ex: taxa de presença em percentagem) são&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;recalculadas e atualizadas automaticamente em &lt;i data-path-to-node=&quot;1,8,1,2&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;144&quot;&gt;background&lt;/i&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;1,8,1,4&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;3. O histórico passa a estar visível na área pessoal do atleta e nos painéis de desempenho gerenciais.&lt;/p&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="270" width="1260" x="490" y="120" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="ZR-NAflUI1GGsINpZlQH-35" parent="1" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=light-dark(#A20025,#FFFFFF);strokeColor=light-dark(#000000,#000000);strokeWidth=3;fontColor=light-dark(#000000,#000000);align=left;verticalAlign=middle;fontSize=25;" value="&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;1,9,1,0&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;1. A interface de registo para os treinadores deve ser responsiva e otimizada para uso em telemóveis (ex:&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;lista com botões de alternância rápida - Presente/Falta) para facilitar o uso no campo/pavilhão.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;1,9,1,2&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;2. O sistema deve carregar automaticamente a lista de chamada com todos os atletas previstos para&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;aquela sessão.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;1,9,1,4&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;3. O atleta/encarregado deve conseguir visualizar o motivo (caso tenha sido introduzido pelo treinador) e a&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;tipologia de eventuais faltas no seu histórico pessoal.&lt;/p&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="290" width="1260" x="490" y="390" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
      </root>
    </mxGraphModel>
  </diagram>
